Source: pgvector
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/pgvector/pgvector

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgvector
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgvector
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Open-source vector similarity search for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
  pgvector adds vector data types, similarity operators, and ANN/IVF/HNSW
  index support to PostgreSQL for embedding storage and semantic search
  workloads.
